  "headline": "WebGPU",
  "description": "WebGPU is the next-generation graphics and compute API for the web, succeeding WebGL. Based on modern GPU APIs (Vulkan, Metal, Direct3D 12), it provides lower-level access for better performance, compute shaders, and explicit resource management.",
